'''德国－塞尔维亚关系'''是[[德国|德国]]和[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]之间的外交关系。两国于1879年1月18日建立了外交关系。德国在[[贝尔格莱德|贝尔格莱德]]设有大使馆。塞尔维亚在[[柏林|柏林]]设有大使馆，此外还设立了5个总领事馆（位于[[法兰克福|法兰克福]]、[[汉堡|汉堡]]、[[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]]、[[斯图加特|斯图加特]]和[[杜塞尔多夫|杜塞尔多夫]]）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://berlin.mfa.gov.rs/ |title=Serbian embassy in Berlin (in German and Serbian only) |publisher=[[Embassy_of_Serbia,_Berlin|Embassy of Serbia, Berlin]] |access-date=2010-12-31 |archive-date=2012-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107063651/http://berlin.mfa.gov.rs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.konzulati-rs.de/ |title=Serbian general consulates in Germany (in German and Serbian only) |publisher=Konzulati-rs.de |access-date=2010-12-31 |archive-date=2022-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220219081803/http://www.konzulati-rs.de/ }}</ref>大约有50.5万塞尔维亚后裔居住在德国。<ref name="destatis2">{{cite web|url=https://www.destatis.de/DE/Publikationen/Thematisch/Bevoelkerung/MigrationIntegration/AuslaendBevoelkerung.html;jsessionid=2D1A38C0B78AD1BA24ACD1F34DD53520.cae3|title=Publikation - Bevölkerung - Ausländische Bevölkerung - Statistisches Bundesamt (Destatis)|publisher=destatis.de|accessdate=2015-08-30|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315025540/https://www.destatis.de/DE/Publikationen/Thematisch/Bevoelkerung/MigrationIntegration/AuslaendBevoelkerung.html;jsessionid=2D1A38C0B78AD1BA24ACD1F34DD53520.cae3|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

